@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xxcnlf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(v1)
    tmp = v1
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.70 / v0 + 0.94)) - wp.sin(0.71))
    v2 = 0.73
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.75 / v2 + 0.24)) * v0)
    v2 = 0.35
    data[tid] = v0
